title: SMT. NIDHI KUMARI vs SH. ARCHIT BHARTIYA
doc: IN THE SUPREME COURT OF INDIA CIVIL ORIGINAL JURISDICTION IA No. 126399/2021 IN Transfer Petition (Civil) No.1427/2018 SMT. NIDHI KUMARI Petitioner VERSUS SH. ARCHIT BHARTIYA Respondent O R D E R Learned counsel for the applicant states that he has instructions to withdraw the Transfer Petition for which he has also moved I.A. No. 126399 of 2021. Accordingly, the said application is allowed and the Transfer Petition is dismissed as withdrawn. .................................J. [VIKRAM NATH] NEW DELHI; NOVEMBER 12, 2021
author: HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE VIKRAM NATH
